code: public static TypeCode forName(String name) {     String searchingFor = name.toUpperCase().     TypeCode[] tcs = values().     for (int i = 1. i < tcs.length. i++) {         if (tcs[i].name().equals(searchingFor)) {             return tcs[i].         }     }     return OBJECT. }

public static TypeCode forClass(Class<?> clazz) {     TypeCode[] allValues = TypeCode.values().     for (TypeCode typeCode : allValues) {         if (clazz == typeCode.getType()) {             return typeCode.         }     }     return OBJECT. }
